OL,4,Crecognising Palestine would break
OL,5,Cinternational law
OL,7,FA minister has rejected claims that
OL,8,Fplans to recognise a Palestinian state
OL,9,Fwould break international law.
OL,11,FBusiness minister Gareth Thomas told
OL,12,FITV News that the decision is a
OL,13,F"political judgement", after a group
OL,14,Fof peers raised concerns about the
OL,15,Fprime minister's announcement.
OL,17,FSome 38 members of the House of Lords,
OL,18,Fincluding some of the UK's most
OL,19,Feminent lawyers, have written to
OL,20,FAttorney General Lord Hermer.
