OL,7,F"Over 140 countries have already
OL,8,Frecognised the state of Palestine.
OL,10,F"And in the end, it is a political
OL,11,Fjudgement that has to be made about
OL,12,Fwhether to recognise a state or not.
OL,14,F"The prime minister has been very
OL,15,Fclear this week and certainly has led
OL,16,Fthe way in conversations with
OL,17,Fcountries such as Canada, which have
OL,18,Falso just confirmed their intention to
OL,19,Frecognise the state of Palestine."
