OL,7,FThomas said that the UK will recognise
OL,8,Fthe state of Palestine in September at
OL,9,Fthe UN General Assembly, "unless there
OL,10,Fis an end to the violence, unless the
OL,11,Faid that is necessary gets in, and
OL,12,Funless Israel commits to a two-state
OL,13,Fsolution."
