OL,14,Fsigned the letter are Lord Pannick,
OL,15,Fwho represented the previous
OL,16,Fgovernment at the Supreme Court over
OL,17,Fits Rwanda scheme, as well as KCs Lord
OL,18,FVerdirame and Lord Faulks.
