OL,7,FStarmer told ITV News he does
OL,8,F"particularly listen" to hostages,
OL,9,Fafter he was criticised by British-
OL,10,FIsraeli former hostage Emily Damari
OL,11,Fover the government's plans
OL,13,FSome of the British-Israeli hostages,
OL,14,Fincluding Emily Damari, have also
OL,15,Fcriticised Starmer over the
OL,16,Fgovernment's plans.
OL,18,FIn a post on X, Damari said the move
OL,19,F"does not advance peace - it risks
OL,20,Frewarding terror".
