OL,7,FIn response, Starmer told ITV News he
OL,8,Fdoes "particularly listen" to hostages.
OL,10,F"I particularly listen to the
OL,11,Fhostages, Emily Damari, who I have
OL,12,Fspoken to, ` I've met her mother a
OL,13,Fnumber of times, and they've been
OL,14,Fthrough the most awful, awful
OL,15,Fexperience for Emily and for her
OL,16,Fmother," he said.
OL,18,F"And that's why I've been absolutely
OL,19,Fclear and steadfast that we must have
OL,20,Fthe remaining hostages released.
